ZH: 我喜欢在大自然中散步，可以让我的思绪更加开阔。
EN: I enjoy taking a walk in nature, it helps broaden my mind.

ZH: 她一直梦想能够到世界各地旅行，开阔自己的眼界。
EN: She has always dreamed of traveling around the world to broaden her horizons.

